flowchart TD
    PROJ[Existing Project] --> DISC[Discovery]
    DISC --> HIST[Historical Analysis]
    HIST --> CURR[Current State Assessment]
    CURR --> GAP[Gap Analysis]
    GAP --> PROP[Recovery Proposal]
    PROP --> BASE[New Baseline]
    
    GAP -->|gaps found| REC{Recovery Mode}
    REC -->|Option 1| MIN[Minimal Cleanup]
    REC -->|Option 2| MOD[Moderate Re-Baselining]
    REC -->|Option 3| FULL[Full Reconstitution]
    
    MIN --> BASE
    MOD --> BASE
    FULL --> BASE
    
    BASE --> GOV[Governed Project]
    
    style PROJ fill:#ff9,stroke:#333
    style GOV fill:#9f9,stroke:#333
    style GAP fill:#f99,stroke:#333
    style REC fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
